%% Withdrawal settlement decision tree (simplified)
flowchart TD
    A[afterRemoveLiquidity] --> B{Tranche?}
    B -->|Senior| C[IL from ILMath.ilForRange]
    B -->|Junior| D[IL + fee share + vested]

    C --> E{juniorReserve >= IL?}
    E -->|Yes| F[Buffer pays IL<br/>Senior: principal + yield]
    E -->|No| G[Deplete buffer<br/>Cap senior IL at maxSeniorILExposureBps]
    F --> H[Return hook delta vs v4 removal value]
    G --> H

    D --> I{IL > principal + fees?}
    I -->|Yes| J[payout = 0]
    I -->|No| K[Reduce payout by excess IL]
    J --> H
    K --> H

    H --> L[_conservationCheck]
    L --> M[Burn stLP/jtLP, delete position]
